** Disclaimer **
Following is a list of standard charges. The charges may vary by patient based on several factors to include: severity of illness, response to treatment, length of stay, and other medical conditions. The standard charge per case is based upon the charge list as of October 2018 and is subject to change. These charges do not reflect the out of pocket costs for services. Please contact your health insurer for an estimate of actual out of pocket costs for services and refer to our financial assistance policy if you do not have insurance.
